repository-code: https://github.com/REPLACE-ME/voynich-transfer
abstract: >-
  Reproducible code and result artifacts for inventory-transfer experiments on
  Voynichese: unsupervised glyph-merge discovery, Currier A/B transfer, a
  one-dimensional section/folio register gradient, scribe decomposition, label
  morphology, robustness controls, and self-copying generators. Twenty
  pre-specified experiments; constrains but does not decipher the manuscript.
references:
