    title: "Voynich-public corpus (Lindemann & Bowern), incl. Takahashi et al. transliterations"
    repository-code: https://github.com/chirila/Voynich-public
  - type: data
    title: "v101 transliteration digital edition"
    repository-code: https://github.com/musyoku/voynich-transcription
